      *   초기화
           INITIALIZE    WK-SWITCHES

      *@1  CURSOR OPEN
           EXEC SQL
               OPEN  THKJL0011_CUR
           END-EXEC

      *   리턴코드가 정상이 아니면 에러처리
           EVALUATE  SQLCODE
               WHEN  CO-OK
                     CONTINUE
               WHEN  OTHER
                     MOVE 'KJL0011'    TO  XZUGEROR-I-TBL-ID
                     MOVE 'OPEN'       TO  XZUGEROR-I-FUNC-CD
                     MOVE  SQLCODE     TO  XZUGEROR-I-SQL-CD
                     MOVE 'CURSOR OPEN시오류가발생했습니다'
                                       TO  XZUGEROR-I-MSG
                     #ERROR  CO-EBM03001 CO-UBM03001 CO-STAT-ERROR
                     #OKEXIT CO-CHA-08
           END-EVALUATE
           .
       S3100-KJL0011-OPEN-EXT.
           EXIT.
      *-----------------------------------------------------------------
      *@   CURSOR FETCH
      *-----------------------------------------------------------------
       S3200-KJL0011-FETCH-RTN.

      *   초기화
           INITIALIZE    WK-HOST-OUT

      *@1  CURSOR FETCH
           EXEC SQL
              FETCH  THKJL0011_CUR
               INTO  :WK-HOST-OUT
           END-EXEC

      *   리턴코드가 정상이 아니면 에러처리
           EVALUATE  SQLCODE
               WHEN  CO-OK
                     ADD   CO-NUM-1    TO  WK-AC-FE-CNT
               WHEN  CO-NOT-FOUND
                     SET   EOF-Y       TO  TRUE
               WHEN  OTHER
                     MOVE 'KJL0011'    TO  XZUGEROR-I-TBL-ID
                     MOVE 'FETCH'      TO  XZUGEROR-I-FUNC-CD
                     MOVE  SQLCODE     TO  XZUGEROR-I-SQL-CD
                     MOVE 'CURSOR FETCH시오류가발생했습니다'
                                       TO  XZUGEROR-I-MSG
                     #ERROR  CO-EBM03001 CO-UBM03001 CO-STAT-ERROR
                     #OKEXIT CO-CHA-08
           END-EVALUATE
           .
       S3200-KJL0011-FETCH-EXT.
           EXIT.
      *-----------------------------------------------------------------
      *@   CP차주관리한도기본(THKJL0011)등록
      *-----------------------------------------------------------------
       S3300-KJL0011-INSERT-RTN.

      *   초기화
           INITIALIZE    TKJL0011-KEY
                         TRJL0011-REC

      *@1 입력파라미터조립:그룹회사코드,기준년월,고객식별자,
      *@한도고객구분,TE기업규모구분,고객관리부점코드,
      *@내부신용평가등급구분,신용평가년월일,신표준산업분류코드,
      *@기준한도,기준한도산출년월일,관리한도,
      *@관리한도설정년월일,관리한도유효년월일,여신성관리한도,
      *@외화기준한도,외화신용공여한도,외화한도설정년월일,
      *@외화한도유효년월일

      *   그룹회사코드
           MOVE  WK-H-O-GROUP-CO-CD
             TO  RJL0011-GROUP-CO-CD

      *    기준년월
           MOVE  WK-H-I-BASE-YM
             TO  RJL0011-BASE-YM

      *    고객식별자
           MOVE  WK-H-O-CUST-IDNFR
             TO  RJL0011-CUST-IDNFR

      *    한도고객구분
           MOVE  WK-H-O-LIMT-CUST-DSTCD
             TO  RJL0011-LIMT-CUST-DSTCD

      *    TE기업규모구분
           MOVE  WK-H-O-CORP-SCAL-DSTCD
             TO  RJL0011-TE-CORP-SCAL-DSTCD

      *   고객관리부점코드
           MOVE  WK-H-O-CUST-MGT-BRNCD
             TO  RJL0011-CUST-MGT-BRNCD

      *   내부신용평가등급구분
           MOVE  WK-H-O-INTNL-CV-GRD-DSTCD
             TO  RJL0011-INTNL-CV-GRD-DSTCD

      *   신용평가년월일
           MOVE  WK-H-O-CRDT-VALUA-YMD
             TO  RJL0011-CRDT-VALUA-YMD

      *   신표준산업분류코드
           MOVE  WK-H-O-NEW-SI-CLSFI-CD
             TO  RJL0011-NEW-SI-CLSFI-CD

      *   기준한도
           MOVE  WK-H-O-BASE-CLAM
             TO  RJL0011-BASE-CLAM

      *   기준한도산출년월일
           MOVE  WK-H-O-BASE-LIMT-CMPTN-YMD
             TO  RJL0011-BASE-LIMT-CMPTN-YMD

      *   관리한도
           MOVE  WK-H-O-MGT-CLAM
             TO  RJL0011-MGT-CLAM

      *   관리한도설정년월일
           MOVE  WK-H-O-MGT-LIMT-STUP-YMD
             TO  RJL0011-MGT-LIMT-STUP-YMD

      *   관리한도유효년월일
           MOVE  WK-H-O-MGT-LIMT-VALD-YMD
             TO  RJL0011-MGT-LIMT-VALD-YMD

      *   여신성관리한도
           MOVE  WK-H-O-LNBZ-I-MGT-CLAM
             TO  RJL0011-LNBZ-I-MGT-CLAM

      *   시장성관리한도
           MOVE  WK-H-O-MRKTY-MGT-CLAM
             TO  RJL0011-MRKTY-MGT-CLAM

      *   외화기준한도
           MOVE  WK-H-O-FC-BASE-CLAM
             TO  RJL0011-FC-BASE-CLAM

      *   외화신용공여한도
           MOVE  WK-H-O-FC-GRCR-CLAM
             TO  RJL0011-FC-GRCR-CLAM

      *   외화한도설정년월일
           MOVE  WK-H-O-FC-LIMT-STUP-YMD
             TO  RJL0011-FC-LIMT-STUP-YMD

      *   외화한도유효년월일
           MOVE  WK-H-O-FC-LIMT-VALD-YMD
             TO  RJL0011-FC-LIMT-VALD-YMD

      *@1 차주관리한도기본테이블 INSERT
           #DYDBIO  INSERT-CMD-Y TKJL0011-PK TRJL0011-REC

      *   리턴코드가 정상이 아니면 에러처리
           EVALUATE  TRUE
               WHEN  COND-DBIO-OK
                     ADD   CO-NUM-1    TO  WK-AC-INT-CNT
               WHEN  OTHER
                     MOVE 'KJL0011'    TO  XZUGEROR-I-TBL-ID
                     MOVE 'INSERT'     TO  XZUGEROR-I-FUNC-CD
                     MOVE  DBIO-SQLCODE
                                       TO  XZUGEROR-I-SQL-CD
                     MOVE 'INSERT시오류가발생했습니다'
                                       TO  XZUGEROR-I-MSG
                     #ERROR  CO-EBM05001 CO-UBM05001 DBIO-STAT
                     #OKEXIT CO-CHA-08
           END-EVALUATE
           .
       S3300-KJL0011-INSERT-EXT.
           EXIT.
